Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.55,0:00:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 你们觉得亚利亚公司是什么颜色的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.58,0:00:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那艾莉西亚前辈是什么颜色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然是漂亮的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.63,0:00:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白雪公主吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.13,0:00:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么那么 我是什么颜色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…铅蓝色…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呆呆的颜色？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.09,0:00:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.35,0:00:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 新威尼斯持续着闷热的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.66,0:00:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但今早的空气却非常清爽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.97,0:00:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吹着舒服的风
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我醒来得比平时要早很多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.26,0:02:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长 这么早就叫你陪我真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:24.23,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那个 最崭新的回忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是船桩 矗立在新威尼斯水面上的无数的柱子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.79,0:03:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是用来系凤尾舟的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有颜色的叫做彩色船桩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有着标注特定的民宅和公司的 类似招牌的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一…二～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长 我们现在独占了新威尼斯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这叫大桩 是将几根大柱子系在一起组成的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎么看都好大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大桩上面写有数字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以从地图上确认所在的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回去吧 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:45.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 你好早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么亚利亚公司没有彩色船桩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 我有点在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:06:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你这么一说 也对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我进来的时候就没有 所以也没去想它…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 这么好的机会 就让灯里来做一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:19.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是要有个彩色船桩才…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来做吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个任务太重大了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 说到彩色船桩就是公司的招牌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到招牌就是脸面…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到脸面就是第一印象…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要照着灯里自己的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自由地表现亚利亚公司就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照着我自己的感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:06:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此这般 今天的练习我要缺席了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船桩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所感觉到的亚利亚公司…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是相册
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这张照片…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是祖母？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 亚利亚社长好年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从我所不知道的时候开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚公司就一直存在着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能将那流逝的时间也表现在船桩上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:16.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈 你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.56,0:09:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才在储物室…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.13,0:09:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 亚利亚社长你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.52,0:09:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年的玉米大丰收了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就给你们带了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.48,0:09:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社长那一份呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不弄坏小肚肚 帮你做成玉米粒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:10:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祖母 这个真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 那就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然找到这种东西 真怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是祖母画的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这是你们的前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初期成员之一画的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她当时提出要制作彩色船桩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么没能完成呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能…还没决定好颜色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.67,0:10:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,颜色…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 亚利亚公司当时刚刚开始运作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和那孩子都还看不出公司的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心想以后可能渐渐能看到的 就暂时放在了一边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.12,0:10:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果开始忙起来 不知不觉就忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:10:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:10:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的有资格做这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚公司在灯里眼中是什么颜色的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 夏天的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来看你们了 艾莉西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 祖母 您来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是什么时候来的？我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.90,0:11:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚好到附近有点事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 您能待久一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…有点不方便呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:11:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 下午的客人快要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 差不多构思好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.03,0:12:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…我想今天先不练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.27,0:12:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟亚利亚公司好好聊聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.58,0:13:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,画这个设计图的前辈 是什么样的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…我还是不太明白…亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对不起 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝色 白色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,画这张设计图的前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定也很喜欢从这里看到的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海的声音 是蓝色的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风的声音 是白色的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝色和白色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还把那个设计也融合进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.78,0:15:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真期待完成后的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们加油吧 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:16:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Alright…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请给我红色铅笔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 在弄了在弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 蓝华 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 还好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要我们帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定连猫咪的手都想借来用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.75,0:17:00.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 但是我想一个人努力看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.63,0:17:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就努力加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们超级期待的说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.95,0:17:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道我…脸上沾到油漆了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝色 大海和天空的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从亚利亚公司成立以来就不曾改变的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且现在 将来也不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:11.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 艾莉西亚前辈 你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.21,0:18:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:18:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.81,0:18:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就在这里吃晚餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.83,0:19:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庆祝船桩完成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是用祖母的玉米做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 我开动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 幸福的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在太好了 真想让祖母也看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个人一定很努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是一个人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得那位画设计图的前辈一直都陪在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:48.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不在这里的 那位我不认识的前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天我也会引退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:20:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而独当一面的灯里和我不认识的后辈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将一同凝望这个船桩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候 我会变成什么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.75,0:20:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得有点…害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.14,0:20:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.62,0:20:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制作船桩的时候 你不是感觉到前辈就在身边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.16,0:20:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.27,0:20:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然从领航员引退了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但作为设计者的她 却仍旧是彼时彼刻的她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且同灯里交流着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.93,0:20:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样的 这个彩色船桩将一直留在亚利亚公司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在灯里离开这里以后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这仍是灯里在亚利亚公司的日子的印证
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.93,0:20:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直一直 永远都不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.90,0:20:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是现在的灯里 你的化身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:21:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的 我的…化身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.44,0:21:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.26,0:21:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久很久以后 只要来这里看到这个彩色船桩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.99,0:21:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能见到今天的我们了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.86,0:21:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厉害了 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.13,0:21:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厉害了 艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.16,0:22:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超乎想像呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.72,0:22:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.44,0:22:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.35,0:22:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想跟艾莉西亚前辈留下现在的纪念…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.54,0:22:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始也不晚 艾莉西亚前辈～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.91,0:22:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了 练习练习
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.11,0:22:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟重要的人一同度过的 宝贵的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.18,0:22:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这隽永的一刻 在遥远的将来也能回首再见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.75,0:22:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美好的期待又多了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.98,0:22:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是说 灯里姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.94,0:22:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要看很久以前灯里姐姐写的邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.27,0:22:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能再次见到当时的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.23,0:22:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.02,0:24:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 广阔的圈子中…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:59.15,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}窓からそっと 朝陽がのびて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:12.13,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}まどろむまつ毛に こぼれてくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.47,0:02:27.17,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}そよふく風 部屋へと招いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:39.98,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}木漏れ日に 君の寝顔 優しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:39.98,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an7}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:46.30,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}いつものありふれた朝だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:53.91,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}鮮やかに色づいてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.18,0:03:01.39,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}それは君と巡り合えた奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:04.93,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}ひとりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:11.70,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}君と一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:59.15,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}晨曦悄然漫入窗际
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:12.13,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}洒落在 舒睡的睫毛间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.47,0:02:27.17,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}让轻拂的风吹入小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:39.98,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}枝叶间滑落的阳光 映衬你的睡颜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:39.98,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an3}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:46.30,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}虽是个平凡无奇的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:53.91,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}也染上了艳丽的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.18,0:03:01.39,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}那正是与你邂逅的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:04.93,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我并非孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:11.70,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}因为 有你相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:57.39,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}白い帽子 追いかけて笑う 響く声は高く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.95,0:23:08.93,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}少し早い 夏の訪れに 耳を澄ましたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.61,0:23:16.86,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}ゆっくりと 長くなる影ふたつ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.95,0:23:21.90,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}小さな 足音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.19,0:23:28.21,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}金色に煌めく 夕暮れる空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.42,0:23:33.92,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}波打ち際どこまでも染めて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.04,0:23:40.02,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}廻りだす季節の かけらを集めて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.16,0:23:45.50,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}そっと触れた指先に感じる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.89,0:23:50.85,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}あふれる光の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:57.39,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}追逐着 白色帽子的笑声 响彻云际
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.95,0:23:08.93,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}倾听着 过早到来的 夏日之声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.61,0:23:16.86,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}慢慢地 拉长的两个影子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.95,0:23:21.90,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}细碎的 脚步声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.19,0:23:28.21,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}夕阳西下的天空 闪烁着耀眼的金色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.42,0:23:33.92,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}映照在波浪间染遍全城
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.04,0:23:40.02,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}细心收集不断变换的 季节的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.16,0:23:45.50,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}蓦然掠过指尖的感触
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.89,0:23:50.85,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}消失在泛起的光芒中
